@startuml
[*] --> NotVerified
NotVerified --> AuthorizeUrlBuilt : build authorize URL
AuthorizeUrlBuilt --> OAuthRedirected : teacher opens Discord OAuth
OAuthRedirected --> Cancelled : user cancels
OAuthRedirected --> CallbackReceived : Discord returns code/state
CallbackReceived --> Rejected : missing code/state or invalid state
CallbackReceived --> TokenExchanged : exchange code
TokenExchanged --> DiscordUserFetched : fetch current user
DiscordUserFetched --> Verified : save Discord identity
Rejected --> NotVerified
Cancelled --> NotVerified
Verified --> [*]
@enduml
